ss country trip to attend coz I will have all sorts of questions for him. Not so much about his work, mind you, but questions! How much would the tix be for that one? (assuming he will actually be some sentient and speaking version of \"alive\" for it) ","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"2 months ago","ctime":"March 11 2017, 23:43:47 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://mojave-wolf.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"mojave_wolf","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"mojave_wolf","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://mojave-wolf.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"mojave_wolf","ctime_ts":1489275827,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/91237832/7059164","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/525869.html?thread=25853741#t25853741","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/525869.html?thread=25853741#t25853741","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/525869.html?thread=25853741#t25853741","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"grrm","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":25853741,"talkid":100991,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/525869.html?thread=25853741#t25853741","above":25852973,"upictitle":"George R.R. Martin: Spain","article":"He is alive and ambulatory, and he LOVES to answer questions.  That's his main thing, in fact.   Just go to YouTube and enter \"Ask Lovecraft\" and you'll see.","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"2 months ago","ctime":"March 12 2017, 00:57:07 UTC","parent":25852973,"massac